Running the Plugin Interactive Test

From SCHEDULING/IntTest/test:

1) Start the system with

    ./scripts/testEnv start

2) Delete all projects

    ./scripts/deleteAllProjects

3) Load some projects, e.g.

    ./scripts/loadAllProjects ./projects/01SBin1OUS.aot

4) Prepare the system to run the Plugins interactively

    ./scripts/runSchedulingPluginsTest <Mode>

where mode can be CreateArray, Interactive or Queued.

5) Start the plugin. To start the CreateArray plugin use:

    ./scripts/startCreateArrayPlugin

and to start the Interactive or Queued plugin:

    ./scripts/startSchedulerPlugin

6) Interact with the plugins, load projects, execute them, etc.

7) To shutdown:

    ./scripts/testEnv stop

